Entry.JapaneseText: なんだよ、なんだよ…… どうしたってんだよ!?
Entry.EnglishText: What the hell... What's going on?!

Entry.JapaneseText: こんな地鳴りは、これまでにはなかった…… カレギア中に轟くような……!!
Entry.EnglishText: I've never heard the earth rumble like this before... It's as though it echoes throughout the entirety of Callegea...!

Entry.JapaneseText: ねえ、どうなるの……ボクたち……！
Entry.EnglishText: Hey... What's going to happen to us...?!
...I have a really bad feeling about this...

Entry.JapaneseText: 何が……何が起ころうとしているんだ……？
Entry.EnglishText: Just what the hell is going to happen...?
